            "title": "Infobip and T-Mobile Integrate Network Apis to Enhance Fraud Protection for Enterprises",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><p>Infobip is extending security measures for enterprise customers as a go-to-market partner. Now, T-Mobile?s network APIs works seamlessly with Infobip?s platform to enhance user verification with the goal of reducing fraudulent activity. Network APIs make it possible for developers to communicate with various telecom operators to verify device possession and authenticate user identities in-app while delivering the secure and simplified end user experience consumers want.</p><p>CAMARA Open Gateway APIs are changing this by establishing a common standard across MNOs, aggregators, and developers, removing a critical barrier and making telecom capabilities far more accessible. By integrating T-Mobile?s advanced network APIs with Infobip?s omnichannel platform, enterprises can deploy a seamless solution that enhances verification and fraud prevention capabilities for partners and end customers.</p></div>",
